<plot>Alex (David Bradley) reluctantly collects debts for the mob. Alex has led his brother Tony (Brad Milne) to believe that he is a shoe-salesman. However Alex's real talents will be desperately needed as the story unfolds. Tony has aligned himself with a group of mercenaries lead by Simon (Thorsten Nickel), who have agreed to deter a local scientist from using a faulty filtering system to neutralize chemical warheads. As tension mounts, Alex is forced into action against Simon and his treacherous band of terrorists. Who will live, who will die...only a killer can save the day.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?118974</url></doc>
